item.title: BIG DATA
item.description: BIG DATA What’s the big idea behind “big data”? You may have heard the term, but come on, what does it REALLY mean? And what does it mean for your small or medium-tier business? Razoyo’s CEO Paul Byrne and CTO William Byrne have got you covered. Now, that’s some Big Data energy.
